Maya Package Manager.
=====================

! Found any bugs? Please report them: https://github.com/sakaki91/maya/issues
! Need help? See the documentation: https://sakaki91.github.io/src/maya-wiki.html

Minimum Requirements:
---------------------
coreutils, gcc, git

Installation:
-------------
   $ git clone https://github.com/sakaki91/maya $HOME/.local/share/maya

If you don't have a local binaries folder, run this:
   $ mkdir -p $HOME/.local/bin && ln -sf $HOME/.local/share/maya/maya $HOME/.local/bin
   $ echo 'export PATH="$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH"' >> "$HOME"/.bashrc

or if you use zsh/fish, adapt it to your shell's .rc (e.g: .zshrc) file.
